Package views

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ActionsDialog
    The dialog that allows the player to select the action they want their selected crew member to perform.
    ApplyMedicineDialog
    The dialog that allows the player to select a medical item to apply on the selected crew member.
    CreateCrewWindow
    A window that allows the player to create their crew.
    CrewMemberWindow
    Represents a window that allows players to view each of the crew members' details and perform actions.
    EatFoodDialog
    The dialog that allows the player to select a food item to feed to the selected crew member.
    GameOverWindow
    The window that displays the final outcome of the game and the final score.
    InstructionsWindow
    The window that explains the instructions of the game to the player.
    InventoryWindow
    The window that allows the player to view their inventory.
    MainWindow
    The main window that displays the information regarding the situation of the game.
    OutpostWindow
    The window that allows the player to view the items available in the outpost and purchase the items.
    RepairShipDialog
    The dialog that displays information on repairing the ship and allows crew members to repair the ship.
    SearchPlanetDialog
    The dialog displays the information on search planet and allows crew members to search the current planet.
    SelectPilotWindow
    Represents a window that allows players to select the pilots.
    SelectPlanetWindow
    The window that allows the player to select a new planet to pilot to.
    SetupWindow
    The window that allows the player to choose the game duration and view the number of parts needed to be found.
    SleepDialog
    The dialog that allows the player to allow the crew member to sleep.
    StartingPlanetWindow
    The window that allows the player to select a starting planet.
    StartWindow
    The start window that allows the player to start or quit the game.
